'''Welcome to BilliWik.'''  This is a collaborative hypertext environment, with an emphasis on easy access to and modification of information.

You can edit any page by pressing the link at the bottom of the page.  Capitalized words joined together form WikiWords, which hyperlink to another page.  Clicking on the page's title searches for all pages that link to the current page.  Pages which do not yet exist are linked with a darker background: just follow the link and  add content.

Please make sure your browser is set to reload modified pages.

If you have any questions, please see BillyBob.

----

Interesting starting points:

  * RecentChanges: see where people are currently working
  * BilliWikSandBox: feel free to experiment and change this page.
  * EditingTips: ways of arranging text in BilliWik.
  * FindPage: search or browse the content in various ways